  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Interactive Signage Hub",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Connect Display (UC-Display) is a 21.5-inch Full HD touchscreen designed for modern interactive digital signage environments. Built to enhance communication and engagement in offices, retail spaces, hospitality venues, and public areas, this PoE++ powered display combines functionality with a sleek professional appearance. The capacitive multi-touch technology enables smooth and responsive interaction, making it ideal for wayfinding, announcements, booking systems, dashboards, or customer-facing information points. The 1920 x 1080 Full HD resolution with a 16:9 aspect ratio delivers clear visuals, while the typical brightness of 250 nits ensures readability in most indoor lighting conditions."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Smart Processing",
      "text": "UC-Display is powered by an octa-core ARM Cortex-A53 processor operating at 2.2 GHz, providing reliable performance for interactive applications and dynamic content delivery. The system is equipped with 3 GB of RAM to support stable multitasking and efficient application performance. In addition, 32 GB of internal storage provides ample space for media files, layouts, and locally stored data, reducing dependence on constant streaming and improving reliability. Power is delivered via PoE++, allowing both data and power to be supplied through a single Ethernet cable. This simplifies installation by eliminating the need for separate power wiring while maintaining a maximum power consumption of 27W. For connectivity, UC-Display features a Gigabit Ethernet RJ45 port that ensures reliable network communication and seamless integration with centralized management systems."
    }
  ],
